rows.label: qst100304_msg0002
rows.name: Eh... ehehe... Long time no see, mo...

rows.label: qst100304_msg0003
rows.name:
As you can see, Pupun
is full of energy, mo.

rows.label: qst100304_msg0004
rows.name:
But my airship suddenly went out of
control... and after an emergency
landing, it went putt-putt-boom, mo.

rows.label: qst100304_msg0005
rows.name:
At this rate, I can't return to
Avaritia, and I can't give you
your reward for the food, mo.

rows.label: qst100304_msg0006
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Four Mille-Feuille Rocks,
three Crimson Gears, and two
Fancy Bolts should do it...

rows.label: qst100304_msg0007
rows.name:
Momo?! Was Pupun's inner
voice leaking out, mo?!

rows.label: qst100304_msg0008
rows.name:
...I'm glad it leaked, mo.
I'd be happy if you could
collect the parts for me, mo.

rows.label: qst100304_msg0009
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] I need four Mille-Feuille
Rocks, three Crimson Gears,
and two Fancy Bolts, mo...

rows.label: qst100304_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh! Since I already asked,
there was no need to leak
my inner voice, mo!
